The Moet and Chandon Grand Day Party was an exclusive event hosted by Moet, the international brand that manufactures the sparkling champagne that we love. It was quite a party filled with lots of magical moments. The party was hosted at the Twin Waters, Lekki, Lagos. This beautiful place is located in a peaceful and serene location overlooking the beach. The exclusive party was attended by a number of celebrities. It was filled with many magical moments. Scroll through to see some images from the event. <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-658007 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/IMG_2576_preview-897x598.jpeg" alt="" width="897" height="598" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/IMG_2576_preview-897x598.jpeg 897w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/IMG_2576_preview-487x325.jpeg 487w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/IMG_2576_preview-974x649.jpeg 974w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/IMG_2576_preview-320x213.jpeg 320w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/IMG_2576_preview-640x427.jpeg 640w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/IMG_2576_preview-600x400.jpeg 600w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/IMG_2576_preview.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 897px) 100vw, 897px" /> Enyinna Nwigwe Ini Dima Okojie, Nancy Isime and Waje. Ikechukwu and Gideon Okeke <img class="size-medium wp-image-657823 aligncenter lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Moet-3-897x598.jpg" alt="" width="897" height="598" /> <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-657825 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Moet-1-897x598.jpg" alt="" width="897" height="598" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Moet-1-897x598.jpg 897w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Moet-1-487x325.jpg 487w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Moet-1-974x650.jpg 974w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Moet-1-320x213